{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f0289d873a","title":"污蔑“农民生活苦”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ecc9e29c1c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"f0289d873a"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5704f7fbe4","name":"邵恩吉"},{"id":"82a3f7aa1a","name":"姜纯洪"},{"id":"c08906e6e8","name":"李宝印"},{"id":"ccc3af54a9","name":"郭荣环"},{"id":"efce061973","name":"东北财经学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"02d7a05ec7","type":"title","text":"污蔑“农民生活苦”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"},{"id":"36141c4f38","type":"authors","text":"东北财经学院郭荣环姜纯洪邵恩吉李宝印","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"},{"id":"362b414c35","type":"paragraph","text":"“我国工业发展速度太快，重工业比重太大，这是农民生活苦的原因。”(郭荣环)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"},{"id":"90db6d4b04","type":"paragraph","text":"“不能同意人民生活比过去大有提高的说法。首先，和过去比干什么，还不如和原始社会比呢！你看美国工人都有小汽车，你要知道社会在发展，历史在前进，人民生活不提高行吗？如果人民生活不提高，人民会起来推翻共产党的。”(姜纯洪)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"},{"id":"23d00e6337","type":"appellation","text":"“政府的价格政策是不合理的，因为存在很大的剪力差。”(邵恩吉)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"},{"id":"03d56b48a7","type":"paragraph","text":"“农民太苦了，和工人生活相差悬殊，不管咋的，这种现象长期下去是危险的。”“农民穿一件小布衫、一条裤子，工人吃穿那么好，高级知识分子更好。”(李宝印)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"},{"id":"381105936f","type":"paragraph","text":"“我看见了很多农民，他们穿的那样破乱，吃的那样坏，在我们国家里，他们也同样是人，他们为什么这样苦呢？鸣乎！”(姜纯洪)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"},{"id":"f5fd05d9ae","type":"paragraph","text":"“讨药，光说老百姓迷信，不符合事实，这是因为农民穷，买不起药。”(李宝印)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"},{"id":"6c06e49c89","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《我院学生中的右派言论汇编》（中共东北财经学院委员会编，1957）。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a"}],"page":{"id":"93676e7abd","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f0289d873a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}